The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 US Grand Prix ticket refund begins

London: Michelin began the process of refunding US Grand Prix ticket holders on Friday after tyre failures turned last months race into a six-car fiasco. 

Michelin North America and the Indianapolis Motor Speedway (IMS) said all those who had bought tickets for the June 19 event were eligible. Some 120,000 fans attended the race and details of how to claim were provided through the US Grand Prix website. 

